881d1b552","type":"paragraph","text":"请他对我们的中国同志的立场提出意见。建议是：","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"af4c736de1","type":"paragraph","text":"建议他们采取自主的立场，宣布反对内证，坚持和平解决冲突”，争取和解和协同行动，在强调共产党在致国民党的信和毛泽东答记者问中所持立场的同时，争取主张中国领土完整和独立的各党派发表民主宣言。”","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"68eab78885","type":"paragraph","text":"深夜12点，斯大林来电话：","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"545f1e3d0f","type":"paragraph","text":"“中国的事件是在您的认可下发生的吗","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"3c3e13c368","type":"paragraph","text":"（不是！这事会对日本最有利。我们也是这样看这一事件的！）","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"a263fd7fcd","type":"paragraph","text":"王明在你们那里做什么事？他是个挑鲜者吗？他想发电报让他们枪影蒋介石。","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"fe740add6d","type":"paragraph","text":"①即1936年12月12日发生的西安事变。—一本书编者注","index":13,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"9703f2a158","type":"paragraph","text":"（我不知道有这种事！）","index":14,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"e6f0909de7","type":"paragraph","text":"那我给你送去这份电报！”","index":15,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"93ac340a35","type":"paragraph","text":"随后莫洛托夫来电话：","index":16,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"eb74459bf8","type":"paragraph","text":"“明天下午3点半请你们到斯大林的办公室来，我们一起讨论中国的工作。只有您和马努伊尔斯基，别人不用来！1936年12月16日","index":17,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"ac3b8e230a","type":"paragraph","text":"到克里姆林宫见“五人小组”。","index":18,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"4ca66c0df2","type":"paragraph","text":"（斯大林、莫洛托夫、卡冈诺维奇、奥尔忠尼启则。）","index":19,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"016a3e0c48","type":"paragraph","text":"对中国事件交换意见","index":20,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"8ec49ff83a","type":"paragraph","text":"碳商后同意向中共中央发以下电报：","index":21,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"5524264a29","type":"paragraph","text":"“复电建议你们采取以下立场：","index":22,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"f0f560f919","type":"paragraph","text":"一、张学良的行动不论他的意图如何，客观上只能损害把中国人民的力量团结在抗日统一战线中，并会鼓励日本对中国的侵略","index":23,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"aab66379bb","type":"paragraph","text":"二、由于这一行动已经做出，我们应该考虑现实情况。中国共产党要坚决宣布在下列基础上和平解决这一冲突：","index":24,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"8c85298a64","type":"paragraph","text":"1、通过主张中国领土完整和独立的抗口运动的代表人物参加政府，进行政府的改组","index":25,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"5463cd5cff","type":"paragraph","text":"我们在草案中建议的文字为：”由主张中国领土完整和独立的抗日运动的最杰出活动家来改组政府”；","index":26,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"2a72b0903a","type":"paragraph","text":"2、确保中国人民的民主权利：","index":27,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"1befcfa735","type":"paragraph","text":"3、停止消灭红军的政策，在反对日本侵略的斗争中同红军建立合作关系；","index":28,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"8935a581d4","type":"paragraph","text":"4、与同情中国人民从日本帝国主义进攻中解放出来的国家建立合作关系；","index":29,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"ce609875cc","type":"paragraph","text":"最后我们建议不要提出“与苏联结盟”的口号。”1937年1月19日","index":30,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"8c97cf00f1","type":"paragraph","text":"在克里姆林宫（斯大林、莫洛托夫、安德列耶夫、日丹诺夫、叶若夫）。","index":31,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"1ed1aa531e","type":"paragraph","text":"对中共中央的指示","index":32,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"377bfc9f7a","type":"paragraph","text":"1）对国民党和南京政府旨在停正内战的一切措施采取支持的方针一一团结中国人民的一切力量为反对日本侵略而斗争。","index":33,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"63a90cd595","type":"paragraph","text":"2）询问[中共]中央是否已认识到是从苏维埃制度向人民革命的管理制度及时转变，并由此得出一切结论的时候了。1938年2月17日","index":34,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"6688e688aa","type":"paragraph","text":"我和马努伊尔斯基破叫去见斯大林、莫洛托夫。","index":35,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"68140d1dfa","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林：","index":36,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"cbbc5d1f87","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":37,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"5188bdc408","type":"paragraph","text":"3、中国。","index":38,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"431a39a0b4","type":"paragraph","text":"两个方案：（1）国民党和共产党联盟：（2）建立由国民党和共产党组成的民族革命联合会（其他党派参加）。联合会不要加入共产国际。","index":39,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"ded983da6a","type":"paragraph","text":"援助中国共产党——50万美元。1940年2月25日","index":40,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"820526c941","type":"paragraph","text":"和斯大林同志通话，斯大林称不能接见我去谈中国问题，因为他很忙。没有阅读送去的材料。他说：“很多东西我未能读完。请你们自行决定。我们将提供30万美元的援助。1941年1月13日致铁木辛哥、季米特洛夫、莫洛托夫诸同志：","index":41,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a7d7e10bdb"},{"id":"2b98635384","type":"